    ('131ffc1b-9778-5811-9191-ce98205dfa06', 'AIRWAY', 'Lesson 2-1: Airway', 'The trachea of infants and children:', 'Is wider and more rigid than in adults', 'Is narrower and softer than in adults', 'Is the same as in adults', 'Does not develop until age 5', 'option_b', 'Correct answer: B. Is narrower and softer than in adults', 'intermediate'),
