    ('8ac36969-e7a8-571e-826b-1c8b0e3d9236', 'PATIENT ASSESSMENT', 'Lesson 3-2: Initial Assessment', 'In a pulseless medical patient <12 years old, the EMT-Basic should:', 'Start CPR and apply AED', 'Only start CPR', 'Only apply AED', 'Transport immediately', 'option_b', 'Correct answer: B. Only start CPR', 'intermediate'),
