    ('414585a1-8a87-51c4-96a3-0c319bec6e90', 'PATIENT ASSESSMENT', 'Lesson 3-3: Focused History and Physical Exam - Trauma Patients', 'For an infant or child, a fall of greater than _____ is considered significant.', '5 feet', '10 feet', '15 feet', '20 feet', 'option_b', 'Correct answer: B. 10 feet', 'intermediate'),
