    ('29dc0dc9-5e8d-5e2a-a098-1a49bf5993c9', 'PATIENT ASSESSMENT', 'Lesson 3-3: Focused History and Physical Exam - Trauma Patients', 'When assessing the chest during rapid trauma assessment, the EMT-Basic should check for:', 'Jugular vein distension', 'Breath sounds', 'Both A and B', 'Only A', 'option_c', 'Correct answer: C. Both A and B', 'intermediate'),
