    ('3e373cec-1d1d-500d-b934-cea027abd722', 'PATIENT ASSESSMENT', 'Lesson 3-3: Focused History and Physical Exam - Trauma Patients', 'In a trauma patient, the EMT-Basic should assess distal pulse, sensation, and motor function in:', 'Only the upper extremities', 'Only the lower extremities', 'All four extremities', 'Only the injured extremity', 'option_c', 'Correct answer: C. All four extremities', 'intermediate'),
