    ('63bf7804-fd59-58d6-bc01-70cd7aa8eeea', 'PATIENT ASSESSMENT', 'Lesson 3-3: Focused History and Physical Exam - Trauma Patients', 'Jugular vein distension (JVD) is assessed during examination of the:', 'Head', 'Neck', 'Chest', 'Abdomen', 'option_b', 'Correct answer: B. Neck', 'intermediate'),
