    ('de4a465d-315a-5307-901d-b0b39b61155a', 'TRAUMA', 'Lesson 5-1: Bleeding and Shock', 'The most common cause of shock in trauma patients is:', 'Neurogenic shock', 'Hypovolemic shock', 'Cardiogenic shock', 'Septic shock', 'option_b', 'Correct answer: B. Hypovolemic shock', 'intermediate'),
