    ('a21ddf82-acfa-5cea-9aa8-f8ad51f34ec9', 'TRAUMA', 'Lesson 5-2: Soft Tissue Injuries', 'The rule of nines for an infant states that the head and neck are:', '9% of body surface area', '18% of body surface area', '1% of body surface area', '36% of body surface area', 'option_b', 'Correct answer: B. 18% of body surface area', 'intermediate'),
