    ('387dcfaf-a078-5a23-b7da-8d4a162f3837', 'OPERATIONS', 'Lesson 7-4: Evaluation - Operations', 'When a student continues to have difficulty after remediation:', 'They should be allowed to continue regardless', 'Consideration regarding their ability to progress should be taken into account', 'They should be immediately dismissed', 'Only the instructor should be held responsible', 'option_b', 'Correct answer: B. Consideration regarding their ability to progress should be taken into account', 'intermediate'),
