    ('18e457bf-fced-5de9-b493-6264484c2a92', 'ADVANCED AIRWAY (ELECTIVE)', 'Lesson 7-4: Evaluation - Operations', 'The endotracheal tube should be inserted:', '10 cm in children', '12 cm in infants', '14 cm in 2-year-olds', 'All of the above', 'option_d', 'Correct answer: D. All of the above', 'intermediate'),
